OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FAnd she was emphatic: "I'm not coming
OL,6,Fback with more borrowing or more
OL,7,Ftaxes," she told last year's CBI
OL,8,FAnnual Conference.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday she'll be back for more -
OL,11,Fand the tax rises will be hefty.
OL,13,FReeves will attempt to pin the blame
OL,14,Fon her Tory predecessors. She'll argue
OL,15,Fthat years of austerity, Brexit and
OL,16,Fchronic under-investment left the UK
OL,17,Feconomy weaker than anyone realised.
OL,19,FShe'll say Liz Truss's mini-Budget
OL,20,Fcaused lasting damage to Britain's
OL,21,Freputation with investors.
