OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FImmediately after the election last
OL,6,FJuly, Reeves staged an urgent press
OL,7,Fconference to announce, with no hint
OL,8,Fof irony, she had "discovered" a black
OL,9,Fhole in the public finances.
OL,11,FThis was pure political theatre.
OL,13,FLeaving aside the sophistry, here was
OL,14,Fanother opportunity to declare Hunt's
OL,15,FNational Insurance cuts unaffordable
OL,16,Fand to reverse them.
