OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FRachel Reeves didn't take it. Instead,
OL,6,Fshe cut Winter Fuel Payments - a
OL,7,Fchange that ended up saving the
OL,8,Fgovernment almost no money but has
OL,9,Fburned through enormous amounts of
OL,10,Fvoter goodwill.
OL,12,FIn March this year, facing the
OL,13,Fprospect of breaking her own, freshly-
OL,14,Fwritten fiscal rules at the first time
OL,15,Fof asking, the government rushed out
OL,16,Fan accelerated review of disability
OL,17,Fbenefits to find savings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
