OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FThere has been a long and rather
OL,6,Ftedious debate about whether by
OL,7,Fincreasing employer National
OL,8,FInsurance, the chancellor has already
OL,9,Fcompromised the spirit of the pledge
OL,10,Fanyway.
OL,12,FSuffice to say, many Labour MPs
OL,13,Fbelieve the tax-lock is still intact -
OL,14,Fand they fear that if income tax,
OL,15,Fnational insurance or VAT rise in the
OL,16,FBudget on Wednesday, it would further
OL,17,Ferode what trust remains in this
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,20,FWhere does Rachel Reeves go from here?
