OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FAs it stands, we expect the chancellor
OL,6,Fto use the Budget to address the OBR
OL,7,Fdowngrade, offer help with energy
OL,8,Fbills and lift the two-child cap on
OL,9,Fbenefits. To pay for these things, she
OL,10,Fis likely to extend the freeze on
OL,11,Fincome tax and NI thresholds and
OL,12,Fannounce a series of smaller tax rises
OL,13,Ftargeting pensions, high-value homes
OL,14,Fand gambling firms, among other things.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
