OL,3,CHow the Chancellor misplayed a bad hand
OL,5,FThe running commentary ahead of the
OL,6,FBudget is like nothing I've ever
OL,7,Fexperienced, but perhaps there will be
OL,8,Fa significant surprise on Wednesday.
OL,9,FSomething that hasn't been leaked or
OL,10,Ftrailed.
OL,12,FRachel Reeves needs a show-stopper - a
OL,13,FBudget that shifts the political
OL,14,Fnarrative, lifts her dire approval
OL,15,Fratings and offers a credible path to
OL,16,Feconomic growth in the years to come -
OL,17,Fnot least for investors.
OL,19,FHer hat needs to contain a pretty
OL,20,Fspectacular rabbit - her job may
OL,21,Fdepend on pulling one out.
